[0.25rem] py-[0.20rem] text-xs font-normal leading-[15px] before:hidden aft=
er:hidden dark:bg-[#484848]/30">--eval_strategy "steps"</code> and <code cl=
ass=3D"rounded-sm bg-[#e5e5e5] px-[0.25rem] py-[0.20rem] text-xs font-norma=
l leading-[15px] before:hidden after:hidden dark:bg-[#484848]/30">--eval_st=
eps 81</code> run validation every 81 steps</li>
</ul>
<p>Each checkpoint directory (e.g., <code class=3D"rounded-sm bg-[#e5e5e5] =
px-[0.25rem] py-[0.20rem] text-xs font-normal leading-[15px] before:hidden =
after:hidden dark:bg-[#484848]/30">checkpoint-3120</code>) contains:</p>
<ul>
<li>Model weights (with LoRA adapters)</li>
<li>Optimizer state</li>
<li>Scheduler state</li>
<li>Training configuration</li>
<li>Random number generator state (for reproducibility)</li>
</ul>
